description: Bringing a true Neapolitan Wood-Fired Pizza Oven to your event creates a unique ambiance and a truly enjoyable experience.Be treated to the smells and sights of traditional wood-fired cooking while watching our Pizzaiolo create dinner from start to finish!  The pizza is fragrant, thin, and soft with a slightly crispy crust, and is made with the best imported flour and tomatoes from Italy.
name: TJ's Woodfire Pizza
